Doja Cat's Skincare routine:
1) Tatcha - The deep cleanse $38
2) Tatcha- The rice powder- Classic $65
3) Skin Inc- Pure revival peel $55
4) Tatcha- Luminous dewy skin mist $48
5) Tatcha- The essence $95
6) Tatcha- Violet C brightening serum $88
7) Tatcha- Luminous deep hydration firming eye serum $85
8) Tatcha- The silk cream $120
9) Tatcha- silken pore perfecting sunscreen $65
10) Bioessence squalane oil $38

Ion kno... her skin you guys can see its condition. She's beautiful, but she said she "does this twice a day" at 0:50 during the exfoliation which I feel is excessive and may be irritating her skin. I really feel for performers as they their job requires them to have a lot of makeup on, which can be tough for some people's skin. I'm sure with time and her unlimited resources, we will see her skin texture and quality improve immensely.
